Theo Marca, Atletico Madrid gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Lucas Hernandez, Arsenal v\u00e0 Real \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Arsenal v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lucas Hernandez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lucas Hernandez \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/atletico-madrid-1390.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Atletico Madrid</strong></span>. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 ra s\u00e2n 20 l\u1ea7n \u1edf La Liga, anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal va Real quan tam Lucas Hernandez\" title=\"Arsenal v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m Lucas Hernandez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/arsenal-va-real-gap-kho-vu-hau-ve-cua-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m Lucas Hernandez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7 hay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y 22 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn th\u00ec 10 l\u1ea7n anh \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n 12 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. S\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real Madrid v\u00e0 Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Ramos v\u00e0 Varane. D\u00f9 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Nacho nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao, anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Mustafi. Khi m\u00e0 Per Mertesacker s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Emirates c\u00f2n Laurent Koscielny sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ec HLV&nbsp;Wenger c\u00e0ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed5 sung trung v\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 Arsenal v\u00e0 Real v\u1ee5 Lucas Hernandez&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Marca, Atletico Madrid gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/lucas-hernandez-58788.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Lucas Hernandez</strong></span>. HLV Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Atletico gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico muon gia han hop dong voi Lucas Hernandez\" title=\"Atletico mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Lucas Hernandez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Lucas-Hernandez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Atletico gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Lucas Hernandez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nAtletico d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Lucas Hernandez gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi VCK World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. \u1ede b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Atletico Madrid gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Lucas Hernandez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Arsenal v\u00e0 Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Lucas Hernandez \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/352370-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Lucas Hernandez \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"586","checkdouble":"183052"},{"date":"10:59 29/03","title":"Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao tr\u1ebb Bundesliga \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebf v\u1ecb cho Laurent Koscielny","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/26/arsenal-gia-co-hang-thu-bang-thuong-vu-caglar-soyuncu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.arti