old; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, CLB Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bundesliga, Caglar Soyuncu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Arsenal b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng Sven Mislintat, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Borussia Dortmund v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c. Sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/goc-arsenal-aubameyang-va-bai-toan-hoc-bua-cho-wenger-172-181037.html\" target=\"_blank\">Aubameyang</span>, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y The Gunners \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Caglar Soyuncu c\u1ee7a Freiburg.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gia co hang thu, Arsenal chieu mo Caglar Soyuncu  hinh anh\" title=\"Gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Caglar Soyuncu  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Gia-co-hang-thu,-Arsenal-chieu-mo-Caglar-Soyuncu--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Caglar Soyuncu \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 thua 8 tr\u1eadn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, do \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia Sven Mislintat v\u1edbi t\u00e0i nh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho HLV Wenger mua Caglar Soyuncu, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb CLB Altinordu \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 2,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Freiburg, Soyuncu \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn \u1ed5n, c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecdc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd Soyuncu, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Laurent Koscielny v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Per Mertesacker trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn theo d\u00f5i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 1-0 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CH Ireland t\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal,</span> gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Freiburg \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u201cSoyuncu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3\u00a0 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. Soyuncu v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\nRoboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-liverpool-dai-chien-gianh-sao-tre-tuyen-duc-172-183048.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2014/12/3/Tu-Wenger-toi-Klopp-Can-mot-su-giai-thoat-o-Emirates.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-liverpool-dai-chien-gianh-sao-tre-tuyen-duc-172-183048.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London Arsenal v\u1eeba gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c Kerem Demirbay c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Liverpool.</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"585","checkdouble":"183051"},{"date":"09:01 29/03","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen hay nh\u1e