0 c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng David de Gea (Man United), Thibaut Courtois (Chelsea), Marc-Andre ter Stegen (Barcelona), Manuel Neuer (Bayern Munich), Conti \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i Roma cho danh x\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e8m mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi-voi-gia-sieu-khung-180-182517.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Alisson</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia. Nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Roma \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao: \u0110\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paolo Conti khen thu mon Alisson xuat sac nhat the gioi hinh anh\" title=\"Paolo Conti khen th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/2/conti-khen-thu-mon-alisson-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Conti khen th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/taffarel-khen-thu-mon-alisson-hon-buffon-vi-dai-180-182685.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alisson</strong></span> trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil. &ldquo;V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;, Conti n\u00f3i tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e0i ph\u00e1t thanh c\u1ee7a Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alisson tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n xung quanh. Alisson \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u00f4 gi\u00e1. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlisson ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Brazil trong th\u00e1ng 3 n\u00e0y. Anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Selecao, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ederson \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Man City. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Roma m\u1edbi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n cho Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Nga \u0111\u1ec1u trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/liverpool-va-real-nhan-tin-mung-vu-thu-mon-cua-roma-180-182742.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Real nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/taffarel-khen-thu-mon-alisson-hon-buffon-vi-dai-180-182685.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Buffon v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi-voi-gia-sieu-khung-180-182517.html\">Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-bi-nan-gan-tham-vong-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-the-gioi-172-182442.html\">Liverpool b\u1ecb &ldquo;n\u1eafn g\u00e2n&rdquo; tham v\u1ecdng ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/soc-liverpool-mua-thu-mon-alisson-gia-71-trieu-bang-172-182259.html\">S\u1ed1c: Liverpool chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-liverpool-nen-chi-dam-cho-alisson-172-181032.html\">V\u00ec sao Liverpool n\u00ean chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Alisson?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"584","checkdouble":"183038"},{"date":"08:43 29/03","title":"B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Jordan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","im