a5n l\u1edbn trong m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Jordan \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019. C\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hang thu DT Viet Nam gay an tuong manh tai vong loai Asian Cup 2019.\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/bao-chi-jordan-an-tuong-voi-hang-thu-dt-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Kooora.com c\u1ee7a Jordan b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-ca-ngoi-cac-hoc-tro-sau-tran-hoa-jordan-168-182971.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">HLV Park Hang Seo</span></span>: &quot;\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam mang \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho Jordan v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi&nbsp; nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, gi\u00e0u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Jordan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a nh\u1edd c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ea7u may c\u1ee7a Amarah&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t t\u1edd b\u00e1o kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Jordan l\u00e0 Al Ghad ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee7 quan: &quot;Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e9o nh\u01b0ng Jordan kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i pressing, ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft l\u00f9i s\u00e2u v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh gi\u00fap c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00ean b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, c\u1ea3 sau khi b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft chuy\u00ean theo d\u00f5i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, Gabriel Tan vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Fox Sports: &quot;D\u00f9 Jordan li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu thua t\u1eeb c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u01b0ng \u00fd. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111u\u1ed1i s\u1ee9c d\u1ea7n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Jordan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p r\u1ed3i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-jordan-11-viet-nam-vong-loai-asian-cup-2019-325-182960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/tong-hop-jordan-11-viet-nam-vong-loai-asian-cup-2019.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-jordan-11-viet-nam-vong-loai-asian-cup-2019-325-182960.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Jordan 1-1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (V\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 suy gi\u1ea3m th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"583","checkdouble":"183034"},{"date":"08:39 29/03","title":"HLV Graechen ch\u00ea h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/hlv-graechen-che-hoc-tro-sau-that-bai-truoc-u19-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}