{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen gia Nguyen Thanh Vinh khen thay tro Park Hang Seo hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u00ean gia Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh khen th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Chuyen-gia-Nguyen-Thanh-Vinh-khen-thay-tro-Park-Hang-Seo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u00ean gia Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh khen th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Jordan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 27/3, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0110T Jordan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y \u00c1, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng &nbsp;\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Jordan. &nbsp;&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7p 1 ch\u01a1i ngang ng\u1eeda, s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng&nbsp;v\u1edbi Jordan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n th\u00ec tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngay trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng, pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang&rdquo;, c\u1ef1u HLV SLNA cho hay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng Vinh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, chuy\u00ean gia HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua. C\u1ea3 V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/jordan-11-viet-nam-gia-nhu-trong-bong-da-co-tu-neu-168-182961.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/jordan-11-viet-nam-gia-nhu-trong-bong-da-co-tu-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/jordan-11-viet-nam-gia-nhu-trong-bong-da-co-tu-neu-168-182961.html\">Jordan 1-1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 t\u1eeb n\u1ebfu</span><br>\r\nRa s\u00e2n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb trung v\u1edbi 7 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t U23, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Jordan. 1-1 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111\u00fang c\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"581","checkdouble":"183042"},{"date":"09:37 29/03","title":"B\u00e1c s\u0129 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c khu\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Tu\u1ea5n Anh ch\u