play:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n chia nh\u00f3m b\u1ed1c th\u0103m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019 khi l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 4/5 t\u1edbi.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb VCK Asian Cup 2015, L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Theo \u0111\u00f3, thay v\u00ec x\u1ebfp nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, AFC s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a theo th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng tr\u00ean BXH FIFA th\u00e1ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 chia nh\u00f3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng n\u1ea3y sinh nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1edfi BXH FIFA t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t tham kh\u1ea3o v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u1edf k\u1ef3 Asian Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Th\u00e1i Lan,...<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam co the roi vao bang tu than tai VCK Asian Cup 2019 hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/DT-Viet-Nam-co-the-roi-vao-bang-tu-than-tai-VCK-Asian-Cup-2019-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-viet-nam-duy-tri-ngoi-vi-so-1-dna-tren-bxh-fifa-the-gioi-168-182125.html\" target=\"_blank\"> BXH FIFA</span>, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t trong nh\u00f3m 3. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nguy hi\u1ec3m trong nh\u00f3m 3 l\u00e0&nbsp;Uzbekistan, Iraq, Qatar v\u00e0 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed1i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng &ldquo;t\u1eed th\u1ea7n&rdquo; cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bao g\u1ed3m b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m 1, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Kyrgyzstan ho\u1eb7c Syria \u1edf nh\u00f3m 2 v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf nh\u00f3m 4. Khi \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span>, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i U23 v\u1eeba l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/jordan-11-viet-nam-gia-nhu-trong-bong-da-co-tu-neu-168-182961.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/jordan-11-viet-nam-gia-nhu-trong-bong-da-co-tu-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/jordan-11-viet-nam-gia-nhu-trong-bong-da-co-tu-neu-168-182961.html\">Jordan 1-1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 t\u1eeb n\u1ebfu</span><br>\r\nRa s\u00e2n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb trung v\u1edbi 7 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t U23, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Jordan. 1-1 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111\u00fang c\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; b