50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arturo Vidal b\u00ean ph\u00eda Bayern.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Vidal voi gia 42 trieu bang hinh anh\" title=\"MU mua Vidal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/10/mu-chi-42-trieu-bang-mua-arturo-vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arturo Vidal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-tien-ve-so-1-duoc-mourinho-nham-toi-o-he-2018-172-179348.html\" target=\"_blank\">Vidal</span> s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 31 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5 t\u1edbi. C\u0169ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Allianz Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf Carrick, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Man United c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 chia tay Fellaini v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Herrera sau n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo t\u1edd La Cuarta, Vidal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Fernando Felicevich, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho Alexis Sanchez, \u0111ang \u1edf Anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Chile, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Arturo Vidal. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester s\u1ebd g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi Bayern. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n hay gi\u1eef Vidal v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao cho Vidal m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 240.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile c\u0169ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n&nbsp; th\u01b0\u1edfng cho m\u1ed7i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng m\u1ed7i danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Conte c\u0169ng t\u1eebng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Vidal v\u1ec1 Chelsea. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi Vidal v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuu-sao-mu-bay-cach-giup-sanchez-lay-lai-phong-do-172-183024.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/16/cuu-sao-mu-bay-cach-giup-sanchez-lay-lai-phong-do.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuu-sao-mu-bay-cach-giup-sanchez-lay-lai-phong-do-172-183024.html\">C\u1ef1u sao MU b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap Sanchez l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 David May cho r\u1eb1ng Alexis Sanchez c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man United.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Conte c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n ca ng\u1ee3i Vidal l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn binh. Nh\u01b0ng ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vidal c\u1ee7a Conte. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Ross Barkley t\u1eeb Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i r\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArturo Vidal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 con thoi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0 Vidal s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"576","checkdouble":"183025"},{"date":"06:18 29/03","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 29/3: Ibrahimovic tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Man United","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-293-ibrahimovic-tro-ve-man-united.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1