font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 29/3.</strong></h2>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ibrahimovic tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Man United. </strong>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, m\u00e0 anh ch\u1ec9 quay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/zlatan-ibrahimovic-44592.html\">Ibra</span> \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Manchester-United-1.html\">M.U</span> \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;t\u00ednh s\u1ed5&rdquo; v\u1edbi Eric Bailly, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng d\u00f2ng comment: &ldquo;C\u00fat \u0111i&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin bong da sang 293 Ibrahimovic tro ve MU hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 293 Ibrahimovic tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/ibra.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1: Ibra t\u00ednh s\u1ed5 v\u1edbi Bailly</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>FIFA s\u1ebd si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c. </strong>Theo ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a FIFA, c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c s\u1ebd \u0111i\u1ec1u tra ngay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t, n\u1ebfu ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0o ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu gi\u1eefa Nga vs Ph\u00e1p, 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ousmane Dembele v\u00e0 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Jorginho m\u1edf c\u1eeda \u0111\u1ebfn Premier League. </strong>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Manchester-United-1.html\">Man United</span>, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Liverpool-2.html\">Liverpool</span> v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c Brazil \u0111ang l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Napoli, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sao MU g\u1eedi l\u1eddi chia tay Ibra.</strong> Sau c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, trung v\u1ec7 Phil Jones c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/zlatan-ibrahimovic-44592.html\">Zlatan</span> qu\u00e1 \u1ea3o di\u1ec7u. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng. MU s\u1ebd nh\u1edb Ibra. Anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, Ibra c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u00fac anh \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn trong cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Man City chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n Sterling. </strong>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, Raheem Sterling \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man xanh. Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa 2 b\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, d\u00f9 Sterling m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua 2 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Man-City-1471.html\">Etihad</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1: Man City mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Sterling\" title=\"Guardiola va Sterling\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/sterling-bi-guardiola-doa-giet-sau-tran-vs-crystal-palace.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><strong>Guardiola mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Sterling</strong></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Doucoure c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. </strong>M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Liverpool-2.html\">Liverpool</span>, Tottenham v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Arsenal-4.html\">Arsenal</span> theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, Abdoulaye Doucoure \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Watford h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, d\u00f9 anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"575","checkdouble":"183026"},{"date":"06:56 29/03","title":"\u201cV\u1edbi Messi-Ronaldo, b\u1ea1n gi\u1ecfi l\u1eafm c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/21/voi-messironaldo-ban-gioi-lam-cung-chi-dung-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index: