:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil lu\u00f4n mong ch\u1edd t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Carlos th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/neymar-44369.html\">Neymar</span> \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi PSG v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 222 tri\u1ec7u euro, tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Messi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Neymar gi\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Carlos n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Neymar gi\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng\" title=\"R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Neymar gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, b\u1edfi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/hlv-brazil-danh-gia-cao-tam-quan-trong-cua-sieu-sao-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><strong>Carlos n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Neymar gi\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng</strong></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i. PSG b\u1ecb Real Madrid lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Cup C1, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Neymar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Roberto Carlos cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi PSG. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/lionel-messi-44368.html\">Messi</span>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t khi Messi &ndash; <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\">Ronaldo</span> v\u1eabn \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ed1 l\u1eafm Neymar c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2m Brazil) \u0111\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng Neymar s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. \u1ede Brazil, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o v\u00e0 tin r\u1eb1ng, ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u00ecnh c\u1edd. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Neymar s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\">World Cup 2018</span>. Brazil \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Selecao c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i trong tay m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roberto Carlos ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Neymar, v\u00e0 Gabriel Jesus s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Jesus s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i v\u00ec Neymar, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Jesus s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.&rsquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jesus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Neymar gi\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng\" title=\"Jesus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Neymar ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><strong>Jesus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Neymar ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n</strong></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Karim Benzema v\u00e0 Cris Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Jesus v\u00e0 Neymar s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o&rdquo; &ndash; h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar gi\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-tuc-world-cup/brazil-ma-khong-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-thi-vut-439-182612.html\">Brazil v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span>, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Brazil n\u00e0o c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Neymar ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-01-brazil-man-rua-nhuc-nhe-nhang-421-182968.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/duc-01-brazil-man-rua-nhuc-nhe-nhang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-01-brazil-man-rua-nhuc-nhe-nhang-421-182968.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Brazil: M\u00e0n r\u1eeda nh\u1ee5c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t Selecao-kh\u00f4ng-Neymar xem ra v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 khi \u0111\u00eam qua \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"574","checkdouble":"183029"},{"date":"09:25 29/03","title":"Barca thi\u1ec7t qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/29/lucas-digne-cua-barca-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-as-roma.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:no