v\u1edbi AS Roma.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/digne-mua-truoc-barca-choi-tot-hon-real-180-162462.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Lucas Digne</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Barcelona bao g\u1ed3m m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 c\u1ed1 nh\u00e2n AS Roma t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2015/16, Digne t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Roma d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain. Ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 16,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 4 tri\u1ec7u n\u1eefa t\u00f9y v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Digne cua Barca chan thuong truoc them dai chien AS Roma hinh anh\" title=\"Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn AS Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/lucas-digne-cua-barca-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-as-roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Roma ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed \u0111\u00f3. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi khi t\u1edbi Barca, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/sao-xit-barca-quyet-bam-tru-o-lai-san-nou-camp-180-162442.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Lucas Digne</strong></span> kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Jordi Alba v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y. Digne ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n khi Alba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c Barca c\u1ea7n xoay v\u00f2ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb thay ra s\u1edbm v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n Barca c\u1ea7n Digne nh\u1ea5t, anh l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i tai n\u1ea1n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Nga, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i. Anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Les Bleus tr\u00ean x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-nga-vs-phap-22h50-ngay-273-giao-huu-quoc-te-372-182948.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/truc-tiep-nga-vs-phap-22h50-ngay-273-giao-huu-quoc-te.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-nga-vs-phap-22h50-ngay-273-giao-huu-quoc-te-372-182948.html\">Nga 1-3 Ph\u00e1p: Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba</span><br>\r\n<span>Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng t\u1ea1i Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u00eam qua khi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Mbappe m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tay...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra h\u00f4m qua x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i trong 3 tu\u1ea7n. M\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Blaugrana \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng: &ldquo;Lucas Digne \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB sau \u0111\u1ee3t thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i. Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 4 cho bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong 3 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Digne s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Barca. Ch\u00fang bao g\u1ed3m 3 t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u1edbi Sevilla, Leganes, Valencia v\u00e0 2 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Roma. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Digne k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua v\u1edbi Sevilla v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 21 th\u00e1ng 4 t\u1edbi c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/phan-doi-loi-choi-barca-thoi-valverde-la-trach-nhiem-cua-cules-180-182988.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i &ldquo;Valvelona&rdquo; l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c cules</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldinho-giai-thich-nguyen-nhan-bo-mu-chon-barca-184-183012.html\">Ronaldinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n b\u1ecf MU, ch\u1ecdn Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-danh-tinh-3-clb-mua-ousmane-dembele-cua-barca-180-182979.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh t\u00ednh 3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia s\u0103n &ldquo;bom x\u1ecbt&rdquo; Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xuat-hien-rao-can-cho-chuyen-nhuong-barca-mua-griezmann-180-182919.html\">Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n cho Barca trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Griezmann</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-danh-bat-chelsea-de-chieu-mo-luke-shaw-184-182902.html\">Barca \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Luke Shaw</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"573","checkdouble":"183044"},{"date":"07:15 29/03","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, Milinkovic c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 bao nhi\u00eau?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-quy-do-milinkovic-co-gia-bao-nhieu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adConta