ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>MU mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n s\u1ebfp l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Lazio \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh c\u00f3 tr\u1ea7n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa Pogba v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c BL\u0110 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Manchester-United-1.html\">MU</span> mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic. B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia bao g\u1ed3m Juve, Real Madrid, Liverpool, Barca v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Lazio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 bao nhi\u00eau&rdquo; &ndash; Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Igli Tare c\u1ee7a CLB Italia cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Trong m\u1ecdi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 80-90 tri\u1ec7u euro.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lazio ra gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 MU mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"S\u1ebfp l\u1edbn Lazio ra gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 MU mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/mili.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><strong>Lazio ra gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 MU mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</strong></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Sergej l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. D\u00f9 sao c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Lazio ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\">chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span> c\u1ee7a Milinkovic.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea1t \u0111i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Real Madrid ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Milinkovic, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Lazio.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 4 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu MU mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/paul-pogba-44584.html\">Paul Pogba</span> \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-6-bom-tan-duoc-gach-do-o-hang-tien-ve-172-182934.html\"><img src=\"https://s