; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Man City \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/man-city-1471.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u ti\u1ebfp theo, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truoc nhung danh hieu, Vincent Kompany phat bieu ve Man City hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Truoc-nhung-danh-hieu,-Vincent-Kompany-phat-bieu-ve-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Man xanh \u0111ang h\u01a1n M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 7 v\u00f2ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. \u1ede \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng C1, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool </strong></span>\u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0110TQG, Man City s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kompany mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Man City s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Goodison Park c\u1ee7a Everton v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp M.U \u1edf Premier League, sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf Premier League&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kompany Arsenal 0-3 Man City\" title=\"Kompany Arsenal 0-3 Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/26/kompany-2-tuan-toi-co-y-nghia-quan-trong-voi-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Man City, nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Man City \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi&rdquo;, Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/vincent-kompany-44156.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Man xanh</strong></span> c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League: &ldquo;Ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 1 v\u00e0 thua 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Liverpool l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool \u1edf Champions League s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Kompany \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/6019-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Kompany \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"571","checkdouble":"183036"},{"date":"09:28 29/03","title":"Vardy mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Harry Kane \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/vardy-muon-da-cap-cung-harry-kane-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{cl