x}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jamie Vardy mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Harry Kane, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Italia t\u1ea1i Wembley.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111ang t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 Italia, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 47 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-1-2, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng g\u1ed3m 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y Tam s\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng H\u00e0&nbsp;Lan 1-0 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 Italia c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toa sang truoc Italia, Jamie Vardy muon da cap cung Harry Kane hinh anh\" title=\"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia, Jamie Vardy mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Harry Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Toa-sang-truoc-Italia,-Jamie-Vardy-muon-da-cap-cung-Harry-Kane-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vardy ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi H\u00e0 Lan, Rashford v\u00e0 Sterling \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Italia \u00f4ng Southgate \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, theo \u0111\u00f3 Vardy s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng Sterling tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Vardy t\u1ecf ra hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi Rashford trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Sterling.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRashford c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t, anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Italia, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/leicester-city-1453.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Leicester </strong></span>\u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u1edf ph\u00fat 26.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Jamie Vardy mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Harry Kane \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu HLV Gareth Southgate mu\u1ed1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-1-2 \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Vardy s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Harry Kane ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t cao ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Leicester s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng trung phong c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toa sang truoc Italia, Jamie Vardy muon da cap cung Harry Kane hinh anh 2\" title=\"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia, Jamie Vardy mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Harry Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/vardy-muon-da-cap-cung-harry-kane-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jamie Vardy mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Harry Kane tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nJamie Vardy mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Harry Kane, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Italia t\u1ea1i Wembley: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i xem HLV s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Italia, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Sterling, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Kane trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Italia, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m sao ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a nhau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Kane c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng nhau tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng&rdquo;, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/jamie-vardy-52572.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Vardy</strong></span> ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-thua-cuoc-sau-tran-anh-11-italia-172-183019.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c sau tr\u1eadn Anh 1-1 Italia</strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Vardy \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/173827-40942/033100\"> Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Vardy \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"570","checkdouble":"183037"},{"date":"10:18 29/03","title":"Adam Lallana \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/adam-lallana-da-san-sang-thach-thuc-tat-ca.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.a