g>Adam Lallana ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Adam Lallana tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adam Lallana kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool</strong></span>. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap The Kop gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duoc ra san trong mau ao DTQG, Adam Lallana phat bieu ve DT Anh hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG, Adam Lallana ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/23/Duoc-ra-san-trong-mau-ao-DTQG,-Adam-Lallana-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Adam Lallana \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Lallana m\u1edbi ra s\u00e2n 12 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u1edf Premier League anh ra s\u00e2n 10 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u sao Southampton ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/adam-lallana-44672.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Adam Lallana</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. HLV Klopp b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Lallana c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Adam Lallana \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adam Lallana ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Italia, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Adam Lallana phat bieu ve DT Anh\" title=\"Adam Lallana ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/adam-lallana-da-san-sang-thach-thuc-tat-ca.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Adam Lallana ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cL\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u1ede Liverpool hay \u0110T Anh, s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9\u201d, Adam Lallana ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n HLV Gareth Southgate v\u00ec s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh: \u201cTh\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi d\u00e0i. Khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Southgate t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra cho t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Southgate v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Lallana \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/17054-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Lallana \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"569","checkdouble":"183046"},{"date":"10:15 29/03","title":"Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2014/12/3/Tu-Wenger-toi-Klopp-Can-mot-su-giai-thoat-o-Emirates.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-ful