Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London Arsenal v\u1eeba gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c Kerem Demirbay c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp rat thich phong cach choi bong cua Kerem Demirbay\" title=\"Klopp r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Kerem Demirbay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/26/loai-hoffenheim-liverpool-tinh-rut-ruot-doi-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>CLB Arsenal b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd theo tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kerem Demirbay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Evening Standard, CLB <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal </span>m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Kerem Demirbay v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Demirbay n\u0103m nay 24 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB Hoffenheim t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG \u0110\u1ee9c Bundesliga. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111i l\u00ean trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o &lsquo;m\u1eaft xanh&rsquo; c\u1ee7a Sven Mislintat, tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Borussia Dortmund. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho HLV Wenger.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Hoffenheim v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2016, Demirbay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 42 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y, Demirbay n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong vai tr\u00f2&nbsp;m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft l\u00f9i s\u00e2u&nbsp;v\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016-2017 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o \u0110TQG.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t th\u00e2n t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Schalke 04 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Confederations Cup t\u1ea1i Nga m\u00f9a H\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 h\u1ea1 Cameroon \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ec1n World Cup n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Demirbay ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 The Gunners chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool </span>khi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Jurgen Klopp c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#081F2C;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-monaco-ban-tin-hieu-cho-arsenal-va-liverpool-172-182818.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/9/sao-monaco-ban-tin-hieu-cho-arsenal-va-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-monaco-ban-tin-hieu-cho-arsenal-va-liverpool-172-182818.html\">Sao Monaco b\u1eafn t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u cho Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Monaco th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong hai k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 t\u01b0\u01a1ng...</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"568","checkdouble":"183048"}]}